No. D-2595. In the Matter of Discipline of Merl Alan Whitebook. 564 U.S. 1016, 131 S. Ct. 3053,

180 L. Ed. 2d 869,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 4579. June 20, 2011.

Merl Alan Whitebook, of Tulsa, Oklahoma, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, re*870quiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
